summary: My favorite frames from the entire episode is when Scrooge is staring at the photo of Della and himself, breaks down in tears...
question: My favorite frames from the entire episode is when Scrooge is staring at the photo of Della and himself, breaks down in tears and rips the picture up. Then at the end where he cries and says “I am.” The whole scene was amazing and David Tennet did a great job.
answer: Yes, David did a great job from the very beginning of the series.
